{"id": 2311, "genre": 1001, "title": "你对婚姻关系都有哪些困惑?", "description": "对婚姻的那100种美好想象，最后都怎么变成「也就那样」的？（题图来自：istock © Printstock Collection）", "record_count": 3883, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201805021641376nJQAFZlMH2bkN0S.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-10T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 281601, "content": "婚姻既是家庭的事，也是社会责任！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1343921}, {"id": 281346, "content": "为什么要结婚？结婚是为了什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314641}, {"id": 281348, "content": "真的可以几年几十年不出轨，我爹娘就是", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244428}, {"id": 281604, "content": "坐等婚姻制度消亡，个人认为更像是利益保护制度", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318456}, {"id": 281349, "content": "也没人规定不相爱不能结婚吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 604622}, {"id": 281350, "content": "一定要等到自己心性成熟，明确自己想要的生活和爱人的模样，才去想结婚的念头。否则，后悔是必然的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340843}, {"id": 281606, "content": "这些困惑有人来回答吗？想看回答?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251362}, {"id": 281351, "content": "凑合过呗还能离咋地", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1261799}, {"id": 281607, "content": "结婚并维持恋爱提高了生活的难度和质量。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337254}, {"id": 281352, "content": "多年之后～都一大堆人来说，婚姻就是个笑话～～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253356}, {"id": 286984, "content": "婚姻就是你人生必须经历的一个过程，就好像上学参加工作一样。你可以逃学，也可以不工作，最后结果就是被社会所淘汰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372042}, {"id": 281353, "content": "怎么保持爱情的新鲜感呢？我用复旦陈果老师说过的回答一下，随着时间、学习和生活，人都是变的，而每天发现你爱的另一半的一个不同点，日复一日的爱上她，爱上每天“不同”的她", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334991}, {"id": 281354, "content": "结婚多年之后我们不妨想一想，我们真的理解我们的枕边人么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978541}, {"id": 281866, "content": "男人出轨都被默认为正常吗？哪怕妻子在孕期", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345063}, {"id": 281613, "content": "如何在长久的柴米油盐中还保持共同进步的状态", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054519}, {"id": 281358, "content": "对象怎么找到的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333805}, {"id": 282638, "content": "婚姻是不是爱情的坟墓？\n结了婚就有人管了，烦不烦？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348760}, {"id": 283918, "content": "需要爱情吗？需要吗？不需要吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026473}, {"id": 281361, "content": "如何保持新鲜感？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178202}, {"id": 282386, "content": "怎么能防止婚后性生活不和谐…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346739}, {"id": 281363, "content": "结婚是一种生活方式，是自己的选择，别人不该干涉，包括父母，朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340917}, {"id": 281364, "content": "结婚、生子是人生必须经历的吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340916}, {"id": 281365, "content": "现在的《婚姻法》正在鼓励不结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314765}, {"id": 281366, "content": "爱不爱和结不结婚关系到底大不大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1189141}, {"id": 281111, "content": "婚姻就是互相性格的磨合，你会看到你最不想看到的自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 170, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340242}, {"id": 281367, "content": "为什么现在有很多人是为了结婚而结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020759}, {"id": 281368, "content": "生完孩子当天就想离婚了，男人出轨了，婆婆发威了，婚姻已死", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340957}, {"id": 281370, "content": "是不是因为有孩子，只能逼迫自己不离婚，可是婚姻早就名存实亡了，咋办好呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340957}, {"id": 281115, "content": "真的能几年几十年保持忠诚不出轨吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 728, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960030}, {"id": 281116, "content": "困惑？我困惑的是为啥我还单身。", "image": null, "praise_count": 208, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980503}, {"id": 281372, "content": "婚姻不止是爱情的坟墓 我觉得在国内这种环境下婚姻是所有一切的坟墓吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312192}, {"id": 281117, "content": "婚姻中该不该保留各自的生活态度？还是需要去迎合对方？", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340292}, {"id": 281373, "content": "婚姻制度存在的理由，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547031}, {"id": 281119, "content": "没做好准备，就不要硬结。", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617163}, {"id": 281376, "content": "醒醒，对象还没有呢...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912161}, {"id": 281121, "content": "对于一段爱情关系，结婚是最好的选择吗？婚后与不婚单恋爱会有什么样的态度转变？", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221198}, {"id": 281377, "content": "读懂对方好难！预知对方行为也很难！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341021}, {"id": 281122, "content": "结婚的人真的是不是最爱的那个人吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340290}, {"id": 281378, "content": "人自己给自己立的规矩，管理需要", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273038}, {"id": 281123, "content": "婚姻为每个人提供创造新血缘关系的机会，这是对婚姻最功利化的描述吧……但通常婚姻都会以爱来粉饰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132554}, {"id": 281379, "content": "怎么能找到一个懂你的人，怎么去诉说你不平凡的一生和保护好一戳就碎的安全感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341028}, {"id": 281124, "content": "结婚之后到底是爱情还是亲情支撑着继续走下去？", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 430193}, {"id": 281636, "content": "婚内强奸我真是笑了，那一方跟另一方要钱算不算婚内抢劫？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1342877}, {"id": 281125, "content": "如何维持长久的互相吸引？好多年都不会厌倦的那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 537, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340308}, {"id": 281126, "content": "暂时不想结婚，觉得结婚束缚自己，还年轻想去拼搏", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1331607}, {"id": 281127, "content": "困惑为什么没对象?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1332553}, {"id": 281895, "content": "另一半都是怎么来的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345319}, {"id": 281384, "content": "婚姻是爱情的结果还是向现实妥协的结果？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1331457}, {"id": 281640, "content": "嗯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808656}, {"id": 281385, "content": "一方出轨了一次，另一方应该怎么办？怎么才能做到最后不两看两相厌？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738100}]}